==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fumigation
<hw>Fum`iga"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>fumigation</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of fumigating, or applying smoke or vapor,
as for disinfection.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Vapor raised in the process of fumigating.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fumigator</ent>⟦br⟧
